title: Airdrie Winter Music Jam
headline: Live local talent takes the stage
description: Experience Airdrie’s vibrant music scene at the annual Winter Music Jam! Featuring local artists, warm drinks, and good vibes all night long. Bring your friends and enjoy a cozy evening of acoustic and electric performances.

title: Airdrie Art & Wine Night
headline: Sip, paint, and unwind
description: A creative evening awaits at Airdrie’s favorite wine bar. Guided painting sessions, soft music, and great company — perfect for beginners and seasoned artists alike. All supplies included!

title: Airdrie Comedy Night
headline: Laughs and good times guaranteed
description: Join us for an evening of laughter featuring Alberta’s best up-and-coming comedians. Enjoy a full bar, delicious snacks, and the funniest night in Airdrie!

title: Airdrie Farmers & Makers Market
headline: Shop local. Eat local. Love local.
description: A family-friendly outdoor market celebrating Airdrie’s local makers, farmers, and creators. Fresh produce, artisan goods, live music, and food trucks make this a can’t-miss weekend stop.
